Program: Free Thinking
Title: Camille Paglia
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/m0006t8t
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 16 Jul 2019
Writer, feminist and author of such books as Sexual Personae and Provocations, Camille Paglia joins Philip Dodd to talk about feminism and free speech in the 21st century, and how her Italian heritage has contributed to her character. Producer: Craig Templeton Smith Image Credit: Michael Lionstar Show less